descriptionHtml:
*now with The Sir\'s unique equipments and 2 new starts - action and scenic (incredible!)

People are raving:

\"His story is like a story you need to be read to like on masterpiece theater\"

\"Absolutely masterful.\'

\"It\'s rare to see such a stoic and erect pose. \"

\"the haircut makes him special. But really when you think about it, it\'s kind of like Cindy Crawford\'s face. Combined with the mustache and chin it creates one perfect face. It\'s lik Lao Tsu says...It has Wabi Sabi.\"

\"This character is Iconic, period.\"

\"All I know is im totally about this guy right here. \"

\"Man.. I need to know more about this guy.\"

\"looks like crab\"



I present you, Sir Phalusis Alphastrike, \"The Sir\" 

A man of few words.

A ladies man. A man only a hagraven can fully pleasure.

The strongest man genetically possible.

A mysterious, beautiful and gifted god-man.

Walk his path and discover his secrets. Firstly, he never wears footwear.


This is a wonderful day for you. My level 46 save file. This has been much requested and I represent it\'s release date to you now. This can be used without any mods - the oldest save will warn you that it\'s missing a file, no worry it\'s just 2 female equipments. Only \'cheat\' is carry weight to match his actual alphastrike strength.

 Wanted in some areas, adored in others - his main dwelling is whiterun home. Also having a few other furnished homes but whiterun is where he really gets down. 

Go forth and adventure as a god-man, as The Sir, The Alphastrike. This is for you, this will be a day.

* game saves are at end of main quest and may contain spoilers
* I am not responsible for any damage incurred to your face from The Sir\'s sepremne awesome
* some photos may have light photoshooping
author: Skyweener
